Ginga Logical Subsystems Manager TODO List
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is the TODO list for Ginga NCL Reference Implementation. If you want to 
work on any of this, please send us a mail to ask about it first.
 
It's likely that work is already started and we can give you more details on
the particular issue.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


EPG
-------------
 It is necessary to create a Ginga-CC user application for EPG presentation
 management.

Context management
-----------
 To implement a Ginga-CC user application (tool) to manage the user information
 and context information. The Ginga Live CD already comprises a simple version
 of such tool.